<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr />

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "Preston_Hall.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>This is the about me page. Needs updated</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
            >
              Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
            >
              Education
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#skills"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="skills"
            >
              Skills
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <%= image_tag "USACAPOC.jpg", width: "100%", alt: "Job1 image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-9">
                  <stong>Civil Affairs Team Sergeant 2008-Present</stong>
                  <p>
                    I joined the U.S. Army Reserves as a Civil Affairs Specialist. Working as a CA Specialist, I am able to help rebuild countries that have been torn apart by war or corruption. I spent a year (2009-2010) in Afghanistan helping to rebuild the local infrastructure and managing companies to build roads, schools and other projects in multiple cities/provinces with my area of operations. I am currently a Team sergeant in a team of 5. I support and train my subordinate soldiers and work with leadership to develop training to insure that we as a company are mission ready.
                    </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <%= image_tag "C21.jpeg", width: "100%", alt: "Job1 image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-9">
                  <stong>Century 21 Everest Realty 2014-Present</stong>
                  <p>
                    - this is what goes in the second education title
                    </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <%= image_tag "bottegalogo.jpg", width: "100%", alt: "Tech School image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-9">
                  <stong>Bottega Tech 2017</stong>
                  <p>
                    I completed Bottega Tech Coding bootcamp in March of 2017. I learned skills to develop and build websites and databases using Ruby programming language as well as the Rails framework. I learned to implement SCSS, Javascript, SQL database management, and other features into the websites that I build.
                    </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <%= image_tag "WGU.png", width: "100%", alt: "School1 image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-9">
                  <stong>Western Governors University 2014-2017</stong>
                  <p>
                    I am currently attending Western Governors University and will be graduating 2017 with my Bachelor's Degree in Business Management.
                    </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <%= image_tag "SLCC.jpg", width: "100%", alt: "School2 image" %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-9">
                  <stong>Salt Lake Community College 2011-2013</stong>
                  <p>
                    I completed my Associates Degree at Salt Lake community College.
                    </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7">
              <div class="collapse" id="skills">
                <div class="skills">
                  <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                    <div>
                      <p><%= skill.title %></p>
                      <div class="progress">
                        <div
                          class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-success"
                          role="progressbar"
                          aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                          aria-valuemax="100"
                          style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                        ></div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
